%% Complaint / resolution workflow state machine (PrintHub). Render at https://mermaid.live
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Open: customer raises complaint
    Open --> ShopResponded: shop proposes reprint / refund
    Open --> Escalated: shop no response (timeout)
    ShopResponded --> Resolved: customer accepts resolution
    ShopResponded --> Escalated: customer rejects resolution
    Escalated --> Closed: admin adjudicates (final)
    Resolved --> [*]
    Closed --> [*]
